name: Yukinoshita Haruno (Oregairu)
description:
This is a character LoRA for Yukinoshita Haruno from Yahari Ore no Seishun Love Comedy wa Machigatteiru.

This LoRA was trained on only 8 handpicked images from gelbooru, zerochan, and screenshots from the anime with animefull-final.

To use this LoRA, include the trigger word yukinoshitaHaruno at a weight of around 0.65-0.8. Sometimes she's generated with long hair, include medium hair to prevent this.


I'm looking forward to see what you all come up with. Be sure to leave feedback as comments and reviews!
